Merry Christmas everyone ❤️ today was filled with so much laughter and joy, we are truly blessed. Hope you and your family had an amazing day ❤️
Matching pajamas was something Travis and I started when we began dating… fast forward to now… Getting Lucy dressed in our marching pajamas this morning brought me to happy tears 🥹 I thank God every day for blessing us with this beautiful baby girl and the love we hold 💗 I’m officially obsessed with matching pajamas haha 

What Christmas traditions do you have with your family and friends? 🎄 

Love always, 
The Gray family
